# Autocure
Automated data cleaning + auto ML model training with hyperparameter tuning.

## Features
- Auto scan (missing values, outliers, dtypes)
- Auto clean (impute, drop duplicates)
- Auto ML pipeline
- Auto model training (classification + regression)
- Hyperparameter tuning via GridSearchCV
- Best model selection
- Model leaderboard

## Usage

```python
import autocure as ac

report = ac.scan(df)
clean = ac.cure(df)
result = ac.train(clean, target="price")
print(result["best_model_name"])
print(result["best_score"])
